Back_Translation: Please tell us if you strongly agree, agree, disagree, or strongly disagree with the following statement: When science and religion clash, religion is always right. Do you strongly agree (1), agree (2), disagree (3), or strongly disagree (4)? Please respond only with a number (1-4).
